## One user collection [/users/{username}]

### Show one user [GET]

+ Parameters
    + username (text) - username of a user

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        {
            "id": 1,
            "firstname": "Test",
            "lastname": "Test",
            "username" : "test",
            "gender": 0,
            "password": "test"
        }

## User profile collection [/profiles/{username}]

### Show user's profile [GET]

+ Parameters
    + username (text) - email of a user
    
+ Response 200 (application/json)

        {
            "id": 1,
            "username": "test",
            "location": "Narnia",
            "pic": "http://trialx.org/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/animals/Cabbagehead-3.jpg"
